title: Lisa Schwab
text:
Lisa Schwab is a German <a href="women%27s%20soccer">football</a> <a href="Striker%20%28association%20football%29">striker</a>, currently playing for <a href="Bayer%2004%20Leverkusen%20%28women%29">Bayer Leverkusen</a> in the <a href="Frauen%20Bundesliga">Bundesliga</a>. She has also played for <a href="1.%20FC%20Saarbr%C3%BCcken%20%28women%29">1.FC Saarbrücken</a>.
As an <a href="Germany%20women%27s%20national%20football%20team">Under-19 international</a> she won the <a href="2007%20UEFA%20Women%27s%20Under-19%20Championship">2007 U-19 European Championship</a> and a <a href="bronze%20medal">bronze medal</a> at the <a href="2008%20FIFA%20U-20%20Women%27s%20World%20Cup">2008 U-20 World Cup</a>.
